{
  "id": "world6_chat_the_color",
  "title": "Defiant Red",
  "world": 6,
  "trigger": "world6_chat_the_color",
  "background": "vertex_village",
  "description": "Party stands near The Color. Quiet, almost reverent.",
  "steps": [
    {
      "type": "letterbox_in",
      "duration": 0.3
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "There was a splash of red against the white. It should not have been there. Red had been optimized out in the third pass, the Archivist had told them. And yet."
    },
    {
      "type": "wait",
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "They call me inefficient.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "They are, of course, correct.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Voice",
          "text": "Are you — are you holding yourself against the white?",
          "theme": "bard",
          "portrait": "bard"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "Holding is the wrong word.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "I am simply not cooperating.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "wait",
      "duration": 0.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "Faith",
          "text": "Does it hurt?",
          "theme": "cleric",
          "portrait": "cleric"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "Yes. The not-cooperating is expensive.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "I was once many shades. Now I am one. One is cheaper than many. Soon I will be less than one.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "But for today, I am red.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "wait",
      "duration": 0.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "Form",
          "text": "We're going to try to stop this.",
          "theme": "fighter",
          "portrait": "fighter"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "I know. I hope you succeed.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "If you don't: know that I was red, for a while, on purpose. That is enough for a thing to have been.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "wait",
      "duration": 0.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "Edge",
          "text": "...It's a good color.",
          "theme": "rogue",
          "portrait": "rogue"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "Thank you.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Color",
          "text": "Nobody has told me that in forty-six passes.",
          "theme": "mysterious",
          "portrait": "mysterious"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "The party moved on. The Color stayed where it was, red against white, for as long as it could manage. Which was — all things considered — a long time."
    },
    {
      "type": "set_flag",
      "flag": "party_chat_viewed_world6_chat_the_color",
      "value": true
    },
    {
      "type": "letterbox_out",
      "duration": 0.4
    }
  ]
}
